'''Summer Spangle''' is a [[Flowers|flower]] that can be [[Crops|grown]] from [[Spangle Seeds]] in 8 days. 

If grown within proper range of a [[Bee House#Range|Bee House]] (5 squares in any cardinal direction), a Summer Spangle will cause [[Honey|Summer Spangle Honey]] to be produced, increasing the honey base value from {{Price|100}} to {{Price|280}}.

Spangles can be purchased from the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|90}}.

